cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

The paper deals with automated localization of anatomical landmarks in medical images using recurrent neural networks. This falls under the domain of computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE). Additionally, the paper specifically deals with magnetic resonance images (MRI) of the head and neck, which could fall under the sub-category of multimedia (cs.MM).
